metadata.name: Happy Family
metadata.description:
I get inspired of this picture from my life.  Every day I have to go to work.  I do not working only on a Saturday.  Some days I'm tired, sometimes I'm sad. When that was the case, I thought. "Hey, but I still have my family waiting for me at home."  That gave me strength to continue in my life.
